{"tid":2385341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：我會正式向美心邀請，希望他們捐贈大批食物及物資，在瘟疫政治下幫助基層弱勢。派發的準則由我決定。","createTime":"2021-01-29T03:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T03:59:27.000Z","uid":271829,"like":9,"dislike":93,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5c79649d04d180bb92f559e1dae1952022e0af0c","tid":2385341,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnuGdgR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnuGdgR.jpg&h=1e3d538a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民鄭松泰：<br />\n【公告】<br />\n日前有一位朋友被警方荷槍實彈上門拘捕，被檢控（老屈）三條罪名。 <br />\n然而，一眾黃絲得知其家屬向我們尋求法律協助後，向受難者落井下石，並因我食美心蛋糕（而我認為沒有問題），甚至咀咒事主抵死。<br />\n本人一向是做實事的人，在網上留言回應意思不大，現公開承諾實際行動如下：<br />\n我會正式向美心邀請，希望他們捐贈大批食物及物資，在瘟疫政治下幫助基層弱勢渡過困境並回饋社會大眾，尤其是天水圍及其他相對貧窮的地區優先照顧。派發的準則由我決定。<br />\n天佑義民。<br />\n鄭松泰<br />\n2021年1月29日"},{"pid":"142bb34c497c326a8d2cfe57503adc56e78546f7","tid":2385341,"uid":154373,"like":6,"dislike":18,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:44:28.000Z","msg":"左膠用大財團d獎學金就得<br />\n蟲太就係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a8fcab9676801886b580d18de15f9e01e76447","tid":2385341,"uid":3063,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"慷他人之慨"},{"pid":"d37bcc99d8e56a4a51dc902f86da5d35fdaeed9e","tid":2385341,"uid":21545,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"忠誠反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d4dedd851e625441f5722966a4691955724fac","tid":2385341,"uid":257272,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"ok wor, <br />\n遲下再R&quot;贊助&quot;派埋蛇齋餅糭.<br />\n局長都有得做."},{"pid":"37ef2a6854aa8232aea7421cae9006ece120d850","tid":2385341,"uid":29947,"like":4,"dislike":1,"sco